description: Its Friday, at 2:55 you hear the bell ring.  You sit in the bus/car and think about your weekend ahead.  When you get home you run straight to the Xbox 360 and put in Black Ops 2, turns out it's x2 XP weekend.  Your headset goes on and you join the party your buddys are already in. Life is good.
